'''Anagraw anafuk''' neɣ '''Udus anafuk''' d yiwen n [[Anagraw amtiwgan|unagraw amtiwgan]] i gebren seg [[Tafukt|tfukt]] d wayen yakk i tezzin fell-as am [[tagnit|tegnit]] d [[amtiweg|yimtiwgen]] niden, akken daɣen i yegber seg [[tafekka tagnnawt|tfekkiwin tigennawin]] meẓẓiyen am ɣef yimtiwgen am [[Amtiweg agezlan|yimtiwgen igezlanen]] d [[aseffud|iseffuden]] d [[Asmil (tasnallunt)|yismilen]] yakk d [[Agedṛur akemdal|ugedṛur anamdal]], akken daɣen illan imṭafaren n yimtiwgen yettusemman s [[ayyur|wayyur]],<ref group="tamawt">Ayyuren ur llin ara d talmest seg tfekkiwin tigennawin, maca yal asmil neɣ aseffud neɣ kra n tfekka niden i tezzin ɣef umtiweg tettwasemma ayyur, acku ur tla ara (ur tesɛa ara) kra n teskanin tisengamin.</ref> anda llan ugar n 150 n wayyuren yettwassnen deg unagraw anafuk, amur ameqran deg-sen tezzin ɣef [[Imetiwgen n gaz|yimtiwgen icafcalen n ugaz]]. Maca tafekka tameqqṛant yakk deg unagraw anafuk tga d [[tafukt]] igan d [[itri]] i d-izgan deg tlemmast n unagraw yerna i teqqen igmamen d tfekkiwin n unagraw-a s [[taldayt|teldayt-is]], anda [[takura|takura-ines]] tewweṭ ɣer 99,9 n tkura n unagraw-a s timmad-is. Akken i tga d aɣbalu agejdan i [[tafat]] d [[aẓɣal|weẓɣal]] ittaǧǧan tudert tezmer ad tili deg [[tagnit|tegnit]], deffir n tfukt ttasen-d 8 n yimtiwgen s umizwar (s unect n wyggug ɣef tfukt): [[Aziweɣ (amtiweg)|Merkur]] (neɣ Aziweɣ), [[Tatrit (amtiweg)|Tatrit]], [[Tagnit]], [[Imzuyeɣ|Mezweɣ]] ([[Amtiweg anamur|Imtiwgen ineẓruyen]]) yakk d [[Yebter]], [[Awihad]] neɣ Asturn, [[Uṛanus]], [[Niptun]] ([[Imetiwgen n gaz|yimtiwgen icafcalen n ugaz]]). 

Llant waṭas n [[Umuɣ n tfekkiwin n udus anafuk|tfekkiwin tinafukin]] i yezmer wemdan ad ten-tt-iẓer s wallen-is (anagar Tafukt d wayyur) am [[Aziweɣ (amtiweg)|Merkur]], [[Tatrit (amtiweg)|Tatrit]],  [[Imzuyeɣ|Mezweɣ]], [[Yebder]] yakk d [[Awihad|uwihad]] akken i zemrent wallen n wemdan ad ẓṛent ula d kra n [[azunyur|izunyuren]] yettfeǧǧiǧen<ref group="tamawt">Timeẓriwt n izunyuren d ayen ur yettilin ara alamma ṭɣaren-d ɣer tegnit, dɣa anecta yettili-d yiwet n tikkelt deg yal kra n iseggasen, izunyuren i d-ittbinen seg [[tagnit|tegnit]] mi ara ad ṭeɣaren gan d: [[Siris (azunyur)|Ceres]] yakk d [[4 vesta]] maca kan ttbinen-d mi ara ad ilint tugnatin wulment war [[abluleɣ anafat]] deg igenni neɣ mi ara ad tili [[tiziri]]).</ref> yakk d<nowiki/> [[Asmil (tasnallunt)|yismilen]] imazrayen neɣ <nowiki/>[[Aseffud|iseffuden]] anda i yezmer wemdan ad ten-iẓer mi ara ad kecmen ɣef tegnawt n tegnit w ad ṛɣen sin akin ad ssegren [[usuɣ|usuɣen]]. S tmerniwt ɣer wanect-a, snulfu n [[Amesaddas|wemsaddas]] (atiliskup) d win yeǧǧan amdan yezmer ad iẓer aṭas n tfekkiwin niden ur yezmir ara ad ten-tt-iẓer s wallen

Imir-a, amur ameqran n [[amesnallun|imesnallunen]] ttɣilen d akken udus anafuk d win i d-ilulen send n 4,6 n imelyaṛen n iseggasen seg yiwen n usigna acafcal n igazen d igedṛuren yettwassnen s [[asileɣ d temhazt n wudus anafuk|usignew anafuk]]. S unect n teẓri ayi, [[Asignew|Asignew-a]] yebda-d s uɣelluy ɣef yiman-is s usrag (ssebba) n [[taldayt|teldayt-is]] anda adad-is agensuy yella ur yezmir ara ad tt-yezbu

== Asnirem d tamusni n wudus anafuk ==
I yigiman (luluf) n iseggasen, imdanen llan ttɣilen d akken tagnit i d-ammas n [[Asedday|usedday]] yerna tbedd deg wadeg-is akken i d-temgarad ɣef tfekkiwin [[tasnallunt|tinallunin]] niden, ɣas ma yella ufelsaf [[Tagrikt tamzikt|Anegrik]] [[Aristark n Samus]] iɣil d akken d tafukt i d ammas n usedday.<ref>{{Cite journal|Azwel= The astronomical system of Copernicus|amaskar=WC Rufus|aɣmis=Popular Astronomy|amaddad=31|tasniwin=510|akala=https://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1923PA.....31..510R|azemz n tuwwṭa=2009-05-09| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20181106183904/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1923PA.....31..510R | azemz n ufaylu = 6 wamber 2018 }}</ref><br/>
[[Nikola Kopernik]] d amezwaru yesneflin tamudemt tamusnakt ɣef tisselmest n tfukt d wudus anafuk.  deffir-s deg [[Tasut tis 17|tsut tis 17]], [[Galileo Galilei]] d [[Isaac Newton]] d [[Johannes Kepler]] gan d wid i d-isneflin irmawen isengamen, ayen yeǧǧan ad ldin abrid i wakken ad tettwiddeg (ad tettwaqbel) tekti n tuzzya n [[tagnit|tegnit]] ɣef tfukt, yakk d akken imtiwgen d wid i kellun s isudaf isengamen s wacu tkellu tegnit. Sin akin deg tallit-a tatrart, asnulfu n [[Amesaddas|yimsaddasen]] d win yeldin iberdan i wesnirem n tumanin [[tifigugt|tisnakalin]] am yidurar d [[Tikucin timnaggasin|tkucin timnaggasin]] yakk d tumanin n [[Tasnignewt|tesnignewt]] am [[Asigna|usigna]]

